channel.title: Real World - devo 7.9 extreme
channel.description:
currently i've been working alot on the server trying to get it much more playable then dodian orignaly came.
[u][b]Server info[/b][/u]
Server base - dodian/devolution 7.0 server version - 7.9 stabilty - tested 50+ players, 4+ hours.
[u][b]Server specs[/b][/u] - note: there is a hell of alot more than this these are just the main updates that people would notice.
must learn combat before you can fight. character apperence screen added on first login 100% perfect teleporting 100% pickup add 100% level requirements added 100% perfect melee 100% weapon weilding includes all new items 100% perfect ranged, added pullback, and launch timers. 50% perfect magic. still needs some major adjustments. fixed repeative animations fixed range up abit fixed npcs glitched hp fixed food healing fixed the ::players command screen fixed some bugs like range not hitting, not giving exp, only now its not as pretty :( added prefect weapon timers for all weapons added all weapon animations added support for all bows added npc's face players added player facing npcs added timers on eating, this also adds a wait when eating till the next attack, like real rs added better way of giving first items, no stupid commands..... added maul special, thanks pk-town added d long special added d mace special added d scimitar special added dds special, took forever! still not 100% sometimes misses a spec NO massing with weapons at all!
[u][b]pictures[/b][/u]
d-long spec [IMG]http://i245.photobucket.com/albums/gg69/killamess/dlong.jpg[/img] d-mace spec [IMG]http://i245.photobucket.com/albums/gg69/killamess/dmace.jpg[/img] d-scim spec [IMG]http://i245.photobucket.com/albums/gg69/killamess/dscim.jpg[/img] dds spec [IMG]http://i245.photobucket.com/albums/gg69/killamess/dds.jpg[/img] maul spec [IMG]http://i245.photobucket.com/albums/gg69/killamess/maul.jpg[/img]
[u][b]videos[/b][/u] perfect teleporting - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BTOXUIzXNa4 prefect ranged. http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZV-au9HKajo (the final product of my ranging.) look around, plus more - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FSpV753czm0
